(I am a print subscriber and even then, viewing of online content is limited unless I subscribe to the full package.  I get the paper part of the week.)  I understand the challenges facing journalism today, but many other outlets have figured out how to give us news without charging.  I'll stick with WFMZ, BBC and others.  Uninstalling this one.
